

	 
       The Story of a Shipwrecked Sailor  by Gabriel Garcia Marquez. This one is reminding me a lot of the movie  Cast Away . Was  Cast Away  based on a true story? This one is and was published 1955. You may have heard of this author if you watch Oprah because one of his other novels is an Oprah Club Book ( One Hundred Years of Solitude ). Marquez received the Nobel Prize for Literature in 1982. 
     
    
